      • changeAccountStatus

        public boolean changeAccountStatus(Account account,
                                   AccountStatus status)
        removeAccount function
        Parameters:
        account - account that should be removed from the accountList
        status - is the new account status
        Returns:
        false, when the account status is already the same status or the account was not found in the accountList / true, when the new account status was set if the account was found and the status is not the same as the new status, the accountStatus will be changed if the account is not in the list a warning will be logged
